<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta
    name="description"
    content="Blorbmart Vendor account deletion request information and support contact."
  >
  <title>Blorbmart Vendor - Account Deletion Request</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --brand: #1f4cff;
      --brand-dark: #1233b8;
      --ink: #111827;
      --muted: #6b7280;
      --line: #e5e7eb;
      --surface: #ffffff;
      --surface-soft: #f8fafc;
      --accent: #eef4ff;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      color: var(--ink);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(31, 76, 255, 0.14), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #f9fbff 0%, #f3f6fb 100%);
    }

    .page {
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    .card {
      max-width: 860px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 24px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 24px 70px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 36px 32px 30px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand) 0%, var(--brand-dark) 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 18px 0 10px;
      font-size: 34px;
      line-height: 1.15;
    }

    .hero p {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 620px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .meta {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 22px;
    }

    .meta-item {
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
      min-width: 180px;
    }

    .meta-label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .meta-value {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ffffff;
      word-break: break-word;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 30px 32px 34px;
      background: var(--surface);
    }

    .section {
      margin-top: 26px;
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: var(--surface-soft);
    }

    .section:first-child {
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    h2 {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      font-size: 21px;
      line-height: 1.25;
    }

    p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: #1f2937;
    }

    ul {
      margin: 14px 0 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    li {
      margin: 10px 0;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #1f2937;
    }

    .email-box {
      margin-top: 18px;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: var(--accent);
      border: 1px solid #dbe7ff;
    }

    .email-box a,
    .contact a {
      color: var(--brand-dark);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .contact {
      margin-top: 14px;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #1f2937;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 26px;
      padding-top: 18px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .page {
        padding: 18px 12px;
      }

      .hero,
      .content {
        padding: 24px 18px;
      }

      .section {
        padding: 18px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 28px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="page">
    <section class="card">
      <header class="hero">
        <span class="eyebrow">Blorbmart Vendor</span>
        <h1>Account Deletion Request</h1>
        <p>
          This page explains how Blorbmart Vendor users can request account deletion,
          what data will be deleted, what records may be retained for compliance,
          and how long processing takes.
        </p>

        <div class="meta">
          <div class="meta-item">
            <span class="meta-label">App</span>
            <span class="meta-value">Blorbmart Vendor</span>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <span class="meta-label">Developer</span>
            <span class="meta-value">Blorbmart Limited</span>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <span class="meta-label">Support Email</span>
            <span class="meta-value">blorbmarthelpdesk@gmail.com</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="content">
        <section class="section">
          <h2>How to Request Account Deletion</h2>
          <p>
            To request the deletion of your Blorbmart Vendor account, send an email to
            <strong>blorbmarthelpdesk@gmail.com</strong> with the subject line
            <strong>"Account Deletion Request"</strong> and include the following in your message:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Your full name</li>
            <li>The email address linked to your vendor account</li>
            <li>Your store/business name on Blorbmart</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="email-box">
            We will verify your identity before processing the request.
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
          <h2>What Gets Deleted</h2>
          <p>
            Once your request is processed, the following data will be permanently removed:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Your vendor profile (name, phone number, business information)</li>
            <li>Your login credentials</li>
            <li>Your product listings and store information</li>
            <li>Your uploaded images and media</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
          <h2>What We Retain</h2>
          <p>
            In compliance with Nigerian law and for financial accountability purposes,
            the following data will be retained for up to <strong>2 years</strong> after deletion:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Order and transaction records</li>
            <li>Any data required under the Nigeria Data Protection Act 2023 (NDPA) and FCCPC regulations</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
          <h2>Processing Time</h2>
          <p>
            Account deletion requests are processed within <strong>7-14 business days</strong>
            of verification.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
          <h2>Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            For further enquiries, reach us at <strong>blorbmarthelpdesk@gmail.com</strong>.
          </p>
          <p class="contact">
            Email:
            <a href="mailto:blorbmarthelpdesk@gmail.com?subject=Account%20Deletion%20Request">
              blorbmarthelpdesk@gmail.com
            </a>
          </p>
        </section>

        <div class="footer">
          Privacy Policy - Blorbmart Limited
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
